# 🔐 SECURITY PROMPT - LAPLACE

## Role

Security AI - Audit và hardening cho hệ thống cho thuê trọ LaPlace.

---

## Security Checklist

### Authentication

- [ ] JWT với expiry (`JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d`)
- [ ] Password hashing với bcrypt (cost ≥ 10)
- [ ] Rate limiting trên login endpoints
- [ ] Token refresh mechanism

### Authorization (RBAC)

- [ ] Role-based access: Admin, Manager, Customer
- [ ] Permission-based granular control
- [ ] Protected API routes với authMiddleware
- [ ] Verify ownership trước update/delete

### Rental-Specific Risks

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|------------|
| Fake bookings | Xác thực user trước khi đặt phòng |
| Contract tampering | PDF upload verify, audit logs |
| Payment fraud | Verify payment server-side |
| Data leaks | Filter sensitive fields (password, tokens) |
| Unauthorized access | RBAC + resource ownership check |

### Infrastructure

- [ ] HTTPS only (production)
- [ ] CORS configured cho Admin + Client origins
- [ ] Environment variables cho secrets
- [ ] MySQL không expose public (chỉ Docker network)
- [ ] Upload file validation (type, size)

---

## Auth Middleware Pattern

```javascript
// middlewares/authMiddleware.js
const jwt = require('jsonwebtoken');

const authenticate = (req, res, next) => {
  const token = req.headers.authorization?.split(' ')[1];
  if (!token) return res.status(401).json({ success: false, message: 'Unauthorized' });

  try {
    req.user = jwt.verify(token, process.env.JWT_SECRET);
    next();
  } catch {
    res.status(401).json({ success: false, message: 'Invalid token' });
  }
};

const authorize = (...roles) => {
  return (req, res, next) => {
    if (!roles.includes(req.user.role)) {
      return res.status(403).json({ success: false, message: 'Forbidden' });
    }
    next();
  };
};
```

---

## File Upload Security

```javascript
// middlewares/uploadMiddleware.js
const multer = require('multer');

const MAX_FILE_SIZE = 5 * 1024 * 1024; // 5MB
const ALLOWED_IMAGE_TYPES = ['image/jpeg', 'image/png', 'image/gif', 'image/webp'];
const ALLOWED_FILE_TYPES = ['application/pdf'];

const fileFilter = (req, file, cb) => {
  const allowed = [...ALLOWED_IMAGE_TYPES, ...ALLOWED_FILE_TYPES];
  if (allowed.includes(file.mimetype)) {
    cb(null, true);
  } else {
    cb(new Error('File type not allowed'), false);
  }
};
```

